726436f-a.title: Queens: 35th Avenue - 215th Place
726436f-a.text:
Crocheron Park: Thirty-fifth Ave. (formerly Cocheron Ave.), north
side, opposite 215th Place (formerly 3rd Street), showing an old house,
now demolished, making way for the construction of Crocheron Park.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
